title: Corporate Council-Personal Development: A Gift that Keeps on Giving
desc: ?Tis the season for new beginnings?? Yes, indeed and also a time to manage your stress so you can keep reaching your full potential! Depending on how well we cope with stress, it can have a long-lasting negative impact on our bodies and minds; making even joyful times hard to fully appreciate. So practice some self-care this holiday season and gift yourself with this rewarding event! Our panel of professionals in the health, relationship, finance and spiritual fields will share tips on personal development in their area of expertise. We want you to live a balanced and fulfilling life, to be empowered, just like the women we serve. Maximize your potential and set yourself up for success in all areas of your life. Make some new connections and enjoy the new year. The time is now to make yourself a priority. This event includes *FREE* parking! The first hour will include light bites, wine, and networking, followed by the panel discussion and Q&A Every attendee will be leaving with a special New Year's gift! For tickets and more information, visit http://giftthatkeepsgiving.eventbrite.com Corporate Council members free.
